Package com.skobbler.ngx.routing

Contains classes that are needed in order to make a route and information about the status of computed routes.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SKRouteListener
    Listener for routing callbacks.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SKExtendedRoutePosition
    Enhanced position class that contains extended route information about a position.
    SKJsonRoute
    Class containing the route as a JSON.
    SKRouteAdvice
    Stores information about a route advice.
    SKRouteAlternativeSettings
    Class used to store information about a route alternative.
    SKRouteInfo
    Class that holds information about a computed route.
    SKRouteJsonAnswer
    Objects of this type contain a computed route as a JSON string
    SKRouteManager
    Class which handles routing methods.
    SKRouteSettings
    The SKRoute is used to store information about a requested route.
    SKViaPoint
    The SKViaPoint is used to store information about a via point on the route.
    SKViaPointInfo
    The via point information
    SKZoomLevelConfiguration
    SKZoomLevelConfiguration stores information about the speed interval for a zoom level that will be used during navigation.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    SKRouteListener.SKRoutingErrorCode
    Enum used to specify route error codes.
    SKRouteSettings.SKRouteConnectionMode
    Enum used to specify the route calculation connectivity mode.
    SKRouteSettings.SKRouteMode
    Enum used to specify route modes types.
